{"tid":757400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白宮顧問：歐盟承諾　將助川普對抗中國","createTime":"2018-07-26T23:01:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T14:37:42.000Z","uid":147314,"like":120,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"38bbdf2328082698d48efae5c13fad70989dfe0e","tid":757400,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T23:01:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201807270007-1.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F201807270007-1.aspx&d=UAQ9pE%2FGVdgdJKmfP0crvkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=bde59499\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201807270007-1.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>白宮顧問：歐盟將助川普對抗中國</strong><br />\n<br />\n發稿時間：2018/07/27 03:58　最新更新：2018/07/27 03:58<br />\n<br />\n（中央社華盛頓26日綜合外電報導）白宮經濟顧問柯德洛今天表示，歐洲聯盟執行理事會主席榮科已向美國總統川普承諾，他將協助美國對抗中國的貿易措施。<br />\n<br />\n路透社報導，柯德洛（Larry Kudlow）接受福斯財經新聞網（Fox Business Network）訪問時也表示，歐盟將立即開始增加採購美國黃豆、牛肉和液化天然氣。<br />\n<br />\n他說：「美國和歐盟將結盟對抗中國，因為中國實質上破壞了世界貿易體系。榮科主席（Jean-Claude Juncker）昨天非常明確表示，他打算在中國問題上面幫忙川普總統。」（譯者：林治平）1070727"},{"pid":"3ca3c549c9b22c4cd6a89e637679e35171d2770e","tid":757400,"uid":141151,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T23:03:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee3fa2cae779b63cb00197d55e169e5ed04f27df","tid":757400,"uid":72457,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T23:05:00.000Z","msg":"消息屬實，中國將成最大贏家"},{"pid":"365ae3b68bd4bd71c3fbcc00fb352914a880c7a2","tid":757400,"uid":41245,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T23:08:49.000Z","msg":"依啲咪唔打唔得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲歐盟左膠，之前仲屌緊美國，扮大佬<br />\n之前仲話要收返美國關稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br